181
00:08:26,959 --> 00:08:27,920
I've seen this one.

182
00:08:28,720 --> 00:08:31,079
The male lead's last name was Li, he died in a car accident.

183
00:08:36,679 --> 00:08:37,639
There's another one.

184
00:08:38,200 --> 00:08:39,200
