189
00:08:45,759 --> 00:08:46,879
I've seen this one too.

190
00:08:47,039 --> 00:08:47,759
His last name was Hu.

191
00:08:48,279 --> 00:08:48,879
He cheated.

192
00:08:51,480 --> 00:08:53,080
