206
00:09:31,559 --> 00:09:33,000
Did you sleep well last night?

207
00:09:33,679 --> 00:09:34,480
Pretty well.

208
00:09:35,559 --> 00:09:36,799
I made you breakfast.

209
00:09:37,639 --> 00:09:38,919
It has your favorite.

210
00:09:40,000 --> 00:09:41,279
Tomato and scrambled eggs.

211
00:09:49,440 --> 00:09:50,480
Eat more.

212
00:09:51,559 --> 00:09:52,879
